  "metadata": {
    "synopsis": "Zevlor is triumphant and emotional after his people stood against impossible odds. If you know he's a follower of the cult, he'll change his tone slightly when turning to address you.",
    "how_to_trigger": "ReCon: oe readyattackondenTalk to Zevlor and then blow the horn.Side with the Tieflings.ReCon: killcombat until all of the goblins are dead.Talk to Zevlor, then he will approach the ladder and begin the speech."
