      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "16",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "0": {
          "id": "0",
          "speaker": "Zevlor",
          "text": "We did it! Watching gods, you did it.",
          "context": "NodeContext: Ecstatic and grateful to player",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "16",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "11": {
              "id": "11",
              "speaker": "Zevlor",
              "text": "They name us outcasts. Hellspawn. Foulblood.",
              "context": "NodeContext: Defiant",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [
                "DEN_AttackOnDen_Event_VictorySpeech"
              ],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "16",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "8": {
                  "id": "8",
                  "speaker": "Zevlor",
                  "text": "But the blood of those who fell today ran as pure as any hero's - so I call us by another name.",
                  "context": "NodeContext: Defiant",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "16",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "13": {
                      "id": "13",
                      "speaker": "Zevlor",
                      "text": "We are survivors. We are family. The road to Baldur's Gate is a long one yet.",
                      "context": "NodeContext: Defiant",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "16",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "15": {
                          "id": "15",
                          "speaker": "Zevlor",
                          "text": "But you have earned every stride so far. Make your preparations - we leave as soon as we're able.",
                          "context": "NodeContext: Reminding of danger but reassuring",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "16",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "9": {
                              "id": "9",
                              "speaker": "Zevlor",
                              "text": "You. I don't know if you were sent here by gods, or fate, or sheer bloody luck.",
                              "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Turns to look at player.\rNodeContext: Normal tone of voice as he turns to address us. He's been reserved before, but now he is absolutely earnest and grateful",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "16",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "6": {
                                  "id": "6",
                                  "speaker": "Zevlor",
                                  "text": "I don't care. You were a friend when we needed it, and we won't forget that.",
                                  "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Cinematic of Halsin approaching the gate, Zevlor spotting him",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "16",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "3": {
                                      "id": "3",
                                      "speaker": "Zevlor",
                                      "text": "Should you ever need it, you have family in Baldur's Gate.",
                                      "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Cinematic of Halsin approaching the gate, Zevlor spotting him",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "16",
                                      "is_end": false,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {
                                        "2": {
                                          "id": "2",
                                          "speaker": "Zevlor",
                                          "text": "But we need not speak of departures just yet. We have time - the road is clear.",
                                          "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Cinematic of Halsin approaching the gate, Zevlor spotting him",
                                          "checkflags": [],
                                          "setflags": [],
                                          "ruletags": [],
                                          "approval": [],
